{"tid":981674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（更正）【回饋市民】15/1 古巨基包25架免費小巴任市民搭","createTime":"2019-01-14T13:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T16:41:26.000Z","uid":77777,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"814e4eeb1d17b99879a4883802da8712f2c6aa65","tid":981674,"uid":77777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古巨基為其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4月</strong></span></span>於紅館舉行<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>《古巨基 - 我們世界巡迴演唱會香港站PART2》</strong></span>宣傳，於灣仔利東街戶外舉行記者會，原因是為了省下開記招的花費回饋歌迷，以20萬元包下25輛小巴，兩條免費車線，於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>明日(15/1)</strong></span></span>在網上公開售票同時，「找數」請大家搭小巴，基仔更預告可能隨時會「亂入」給乘客送驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n基仔花費20萬回饋市民，包下25架紅VAN，路線覆蓋香港島、九龍及新界，請大家明天免費搭小巴，全由基仔「找數」。兩條免費小巴路線分別是來往<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上環至荃灣（中午12時至晚上10時）及旺角至大埔（下午3時至凌晨1時）</strong></span>。25架小巴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>明日(15/1)</strong></span></span>免費乘搭，貼有古巨基演唱會廣告的小巴即為免費，車內還會播放基仔的歌曲《友共情》與《愛與誠》以作識別。。<br />\n<br />\n基仔透露演唱會Part 2歌單及製作上會加入新元素，更希望大家為他集氣，希望可以邀請黃子華及古天樂當他演唱會嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n基仔個唱門票亦於明日公開發售，並採用政府的新措施，首日可從網上購得門票，第二日才會在售票處賣飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LzLvqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LzLvqu.jpg&h=2ae30827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pRxUSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pRxUSa.jpg&h=205c20e1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"50100a7f3da56c346d036c368fe4a3e79d5965ff","tid":981674,"uid":77777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"基仔好波"},{"pid":"b7937b001c265622d0149716009032711d60cb9a","tid":981674,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"可能係呢2條<br />\n<br />\n由上環（信德中心）往荃灣（千色店），途經西營盤及石塘咀；回程則由荃灣（千色店）往西環（修打蘭街），途經堅尼地城泳池、石塘咀、西營盤及信德中心。<br />\n<br />\n由旺角（西洋菜南街）至大埔（太和邨），途經獅子山隧道、大埔公路（香港中文大學、大埔滘及元洲仔）、大埔墟（廣福道）及大埔超級城"},{"pid":"2c91384e28d9c647f3f29432d0d449f3af6fe7ea","tid":981674,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c5e53982f3f4e6d7e4d782574dbf2e56d55b70","tid":981674,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/l5jVA5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2Fl5jVA5.gif&h=8ee024bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36e7b1f45dfee944b70a50ea809cb2313677c050","tid":981674,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"喺CU住hall啲人有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c59ba52025c9ba0a19ed2d4e633bded4d84dee","tid":981674,"uid":36683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbef41ebe4d3ee3568a1f317d6c21365d1d0d03","tid":981674,"uid":105782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T23:07:51.000Z","msg":"我今日就係專登唔揸車返工，去搭紅Van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a6e19c829b3a26f2373c1306a8547abb4d860c","tid":981674,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8dbef41ebe4d3ee3568a1f317d6c21365d1d0d03","tid":981674,"uid":105782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T23:07:51.000Z","msg":"我今日就係專登唔揸車返工，去搭紅Van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 